455
00:26:18.504 --> 00:26:21.684
In fact, I think we're late in the game of realizing that this is incredibly

456
00:26:21.744 --> 00:26:22.154
important.

457
00:26:23.074 --> 00:26:26.934
The original purpose of the NIH, and I wrote this down, this is from a report that

