462
00:26:42.544 --> 00:26:46.124
Making sure that we can do medical research and develop our own drugs, our own

463
00:26:46.184 --> 00:26:49.484
therapeutics, deliver them, and run clinical trials in the US is absolutely

464
00:26:49.504 --> 00:26:52.204
essential for our competitiveness on a global stage.

465
00:26:53.064 --> 00:26:56.224
We are losing that competitiveness very quickly.

466
00:26:56.804 --> 00:27:00.104
We're losing that competitiveness in innovation and in pace of the science.

467
00:27:00.644 --> 00:27:04.284
We're also losing it in the ability to do clinical trials effectively in the United

